# 🏗️ EnergyDNA Global Ignore Rules

# Node.js
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnpm-debug.log*

# Hardhat & Smart Contracts
**/artifacts/
**/cache/
**/typechain/
**/typechain-types/
contracts/hardhat-network-helper.log

# Frontend & Build Artifacts
**/dist/
**/.vite/
**/out/
**/build/

# Environment & Secrets (CRITICAL)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.development
**/.env.production
**/.env.test

# Logs & OS Files
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Temporary Data
**/temp/
**/tmp/
